HEADWORD: Orthoscopic
<hw>Or`tho*scop"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Opt.)</fld>
<def>Giving an image in correct or normal proportions; giving a flat
field of view; <as>as, an <ex>orthoscopic</ex> eyepiece</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

